title: Did Vikings Have Tattoos?
description: Vikings left behind nearly no writings, except for Runic scripts on rocks. New burial site excavations show they also left them behind on their bodies.    TO HELP OUT THE SHOW  Leave an honest review on iTunes. Your ratings and reviews really help and I read each one.
